data_by_age <- data %>% 
  filter(admission_type == "Emergency Inpatients",
         hb == "S92000003") %>% 
  mutate(covid = case_when(
    str_detect(quarter, "2017|2018|2019|2020Q1") ~ "Pre (2017 Q4 - 2020 Q1)",
    str_detect(quarter, "2020|2021") ~ "During (2020 Q2 - 2021 Q4)",
    .default = "Post (2022)"
  ), 
         age_group = case_when(
    age == "0-9 years" | age == "10-19 years" ~ "0-19",
    age == "20-29 years" | age == "30-39 years" ~ "20-39",
    age == "40-49 years" | age == "50-59 years" ~ "40-59",
    age == "60-69 years" | age == "70-79 years" ~ "60-79",
    .default = "80 and over"
  ), .after = age) %>% 
  mutate(covid = factor(covid, levels = c("Pre (2017 Q4 - 2020 Q1)", "During (2020 Q2 - 2021 Q4)", "Post (2022)"))) %>% 
  select(quarter, covid, age, age_group, stays, length_of_stay, average_length_of_stay)
Error in UseMethod("filter") : 
  no applicable method for 'filter' applied to an object of class "function"
